* Install the common way how plugins are installed (perl Makefile.PL, ...)

* Enable the plugin

Set(@Plugins,(qw(
        RTx::HistoryComponent
)));

* Add a new homepage component

Set($HomepageComponents, [qw(
        QuickCreate
        Quicksearch
        MyAdminQueues
        MySupportQueues
        MyReminders
        RefreshHomepage
        Dashboards
        SavedSearches
        RTx-TicketHistory
)]);

* Use RTx-TicketHistory on your homescreen
